{"word":"H5225 - נָכֹון - Nâkôwn - naw-kone' - Nachon","slug":"H5225","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָכֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Nâkôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-kone'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Nachon"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>נכון</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>nâkôn</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>naw-kone'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Nachon = \"prepared\" <ol><li>the owner of the threshing floor which the ark was passing on the trip to Jerusalem when it started to fall off the cart, Uzzah steadied it, and God smote him dead for touching it</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H3559\">H3559</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3199\">H3199</a>, <a href=\"#/H3200\">H3200</a>, <a href=\"#/H3204\">H3204</a>, <a href=\"#/H3559\">H3559</a>, <a href=\"#/H3560\">H3560</a>, <a href=\"#/H3561\">H3561</a>, <a href=\"#/H3562\">H3562</a>, <a href=\"#/H3563\">H3563</a>, <a href=\"#/H3651\">H3651</a>, <a href=\"#/H4349\">H4349</a>, <a href=\"#/H4350\">H4350</a>, <a href=\"#/H4369\">H4369</a>, <a href=\"#/H8498\">H8498</a>, <a href=\"#/H8499\">H8499</a>"}]}